high_descs: Pick the soapbar from the toilet flush.
Turn around and head towards the sink.
Go straight and turn right to reach the soapbar.
Put the flush on the toilet. Pour the water and clean the brush. Take back the brush.
Turn left and again take left and keep the soapbar on the toilet flush.
anns.task_desc: Take the SoapBar, clean it and keep it on the Toilet.

high_descs: get the sponge that is on top of the toilet tank.
Take the soapbar and put it into the bathroom sink.
Turn the water on in the sink and clean the sponge.
take the soapbar out of the bathroom sink.
Put the soapbar back on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Get the SoapBar from the Toilet, wash it and put it back.

high_descs: Turn right and face the toilet.
Take the soapbar from the toilet tank.
Go to the bathroom sink next to the toilet.
Put the soapbar into the sink, rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Place the soapbar back on the top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Wash the SoapBar and place it on top of the Toilet.
